luciole (0.8.1) karmic; urgency=low

  List of implemented launchpad blueprints :
  ------------------------------
  libglade-to-gtkbuilder :    Replace Libglade by gtk.builder 
  cinelerra-export :          Add export to cinelerra file format
  kdenlive-export :           Export to Kdenlive
  pitivi-export :             Export to Pitivi 
  luciole-logging :           Luciole logging feature

  List of Fixed launchpad bugs :
  ------------------------------
  LP: #498619     Acquisition doesn't work on DVCAM nor WEBCAM
  LP: #500649     Excessive CPU use while capturing
  LP: #500158     Impossible to change export path
  LP: #500652     Weird Mixer behavior
  LP: #505288     Error when opening existing project
  LP: #518129     Unable to open existing project  

